---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Communications" description="e-Spokes, Phone Book, Welcome Package and community blog links.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Community Communications</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-10">Stay informed and connected on Thetis Island.</p>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">e-Spokes Email List</h2>
        <p class="text-text mb-3">e-Spokes is the island's moderated email bulletin board. It's used to share community notices, announcements, lost &amp; found items and service information. Subscribing is free, and your email will not be shared publicly.</p>
        <p class="text-text">To subscribe, send an email to <strong>espokes@thetisisland.net</strong> with your name and a request to join. Once approved, you'll begin receiving messages. Posts should be concise and community-relevant; commercial advertising and spam are not permitted.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Thetis Island Phone Book</h2>
        <p class="text-text mb-3">The Thetis Island Phone Book is compiled by community volunteers and distributed as a printed booklet. It contains landline and cell numbers for residents, as well as emergency contacts and other useful information. Due to privacy considerations, the phone book is not available online.</p>
        <p class="text-text">If you are new to Thetis or need a copy, please contact TIRRA through our <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:underline">contact page</a> or watch for announcements about new editions.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Welcome Package</h2>
        <p class="text-text">New to Thetis Island? TIRRA provides a Welcome Package with essential information for new residents including local contacts, services, and community guidelines. Contact TIRRA through our <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:underline">contact page</a> to request one.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Community Blog</h2>
        <p class="text-text">The Thetis Island Blog hosts timely articles, event announcements and classifieds contributed by community members. Visit <a href="https://thetisposts.ca" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">thetisposts.ca</a> to read the latest posts or share your news.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
